item.title: The Power Playlist! with Dr Bolu Eso
item.description:
This week on The RunPod Power Playlist, Jenni is joined by social media star and veterinary doc Dr Bolu Eso.

Whether it’s faith-filled anthems or beats that make him feel like "that guy", Dr Bolu’s music choices are all about motivation, purpose, and power.

Plus, he shares his go-to headphones for staying locked in on every stride. If you want to move, groove, and feel unstoppable- this one’s for you... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/runpod/
